summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Chapter 23.32 of the Seattle Municipal Code at page 8 of the Official Land Use Map, to rezone property located at 3014 Northeast 137th St., from Single family 7200 (SF 7200) to Lowrise 3 (L3) multifamily residential. (Ted and Tonya Jolly, C.F. 307997, DPD Project 3003051)
